Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is GHQ's Public Information Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.11,0:00:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance with Infection Control Law Article 9, Section 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an emergency quarantine is now in effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Citizens are strictly prohibited from venturing outside Loop 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.90,0:00:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been two weeks since then. Tokyo has changed completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The incident from two weeks ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Apocalypse Virus outbreak called "the second coming of Lost Christmas"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}has led to the blockage of the entire city center.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Internet and phone lines are down and the TV and radio stations have gone silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People are now living at local evacuation sites.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Students have automatically gathered here at Tennozu First High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't contact their families
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and they can't go home because they live outside the blockaded area.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, they've stayed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The GHQ announcements say the blockade will be lifted at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But some people, like Yahiro, seem to doubt that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't think the blockade will last much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.53,0:01:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My feet just seem to take me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.78,0:01:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... all over now, isn't it... Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{New OP Here}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I even doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little rowdy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just offering to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're one of those "I can do it myself" types, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you only sweet to your "honey"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with being stoic,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it pisses me off when people don't appreciate my kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's be friendly with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, what are {\i1}you{\i0} doing? To a girl that fell down too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were demonstrating a spirit of cooperation in this time of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! Is there a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Missile Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell what that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell me! What are {\i1}you{\i0} doing to Aya? Perverts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't lump me in with—{Cut Off}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Piss off, shrimp—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nay! I'm just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah right! Like I'd waste a single millibyte storing {\i1}this{\i0} memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:04:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, they were just hassling me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, would you mind leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before, didn't I? I refuse to accept help from anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't look elegant crawling up into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in pretty bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai's death hit Aya the hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the Undertakers will close up shop now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We got separated from the other members when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We don't know where most of our other members are,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Ayase and Tsugumi are blending with the students and taking shelter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Gai... is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kuhouin Group is airlifting supplies in,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we're still in pretty good shape there..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little worried about the vaccine stock though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The effects of the virus are a concern too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to secure a good supply of vaccine. Can we ask for your help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll try to negotiate something with my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you worrying too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The quarantine won't last {\i1}that{\i0} long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to be too optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been two weeks, which is about when people start losing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like there's already been a small riot in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a point. We've been seeing fights within the school too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because everyone's tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of kids who want to go home and can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we could at least give them a breather, that would help...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, how about we do a Culture Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally we'd be having the Culture Festival this month, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding? We're in the middle of a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why we should! Let's liven things up with something big
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and clear out the bad atmosphere here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have enough food to last us a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can pull off something if we keep it small.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard the lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Read the atmosphere, Chief Cabinet Secretary Samukawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry. These conditions will end soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's finally time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir. They said we'd have approval in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life will be boring until then... Shall we do a little preview?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please sir! No more joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't in the same position anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Chief Segai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've both landed in difficult positions, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't agree more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect {\i1}you{\i0} to agree too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess maybe I felt like living it up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this was inside me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you able to hand it to me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During the last fight, I think my powers changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do we put it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try letting go of it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These "Voids" are just one mystery after another, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why are you suddenly so interested in Voids?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll be using this power again, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These conditions won't last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And by that I mean the opposite of what Kuhouin does, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your right hand, its power...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to use them again soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't need those!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't say that. Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that outfit for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They told me this was an Animal Cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really part of the school now aren't you, Tsugami?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, moping won't help anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we have to take this opportunity to have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, where's Inori?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shu! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A live Egoist concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the festival's main event!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the stage directing to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamadate, Minister of Education, Culture, Sports, Science and Technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will show you what I'm made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with this, Inori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, a festival now? There's something wrong with these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the germs have spread to their brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt! What if I were injured!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh sorry! But hey, perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why should I have to—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This too please. And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to do work like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you just gave me too much to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, take this and cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that yucky food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When someone does something nice for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...shut up and accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,St-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, Shinomiya, you're good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Menjo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, call me Hare. I'm sorry for asking you to do this out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I looked lonely by myself...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Shu's changed lately, you know? In a good way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought that must be thanks to the people in the Undertakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuriha Inori, Ouma Shu—everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is way too complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could just destroy this place right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't do. We're in the middle of deliberations right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't make any direct moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No {\i1}direct{\i0} moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, don't interfere. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}is{\i0} this thing? It looks so cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time I see that runt, I swear I'm going to torment her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tenno Festival is now officially open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this fun, Aya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'd be doing this too, if we went to school like normal kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, mini-hotcakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mini-hotcakes, Aya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're having a Cultural Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not right. Not in tough times like this where people are starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a job for us "Philanthropists," am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Humvee and a Gautier Endlave? Are they the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you get those?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was a wealthy man who agreed with our cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:14:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seemed a little sketchy, but turned out to be a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Good guy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just goes to show the high hopes people have for our justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna teach those happy school kids what a harsh world this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you don't want any? These are really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Aya, this is the last one! Here... say "ah."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was {\i1}that{\i0} for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why did you cut it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you cut my connection that day!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could've kept going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could've protected Gai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy... What, so you wouldn't have minded if {\i1}you'd{\i0} died?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I did die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life right now is so half-assed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the accident and now too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna make {\i1}me{\i0} sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Aya. I'll go back to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the music will start, but don't come out yet okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out on my signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She has her songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's not like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just some girl her lost her Endlave...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to come closer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point. I'm not useful for anything anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying you're one of us, so you should be with us more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai died, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I couldn't protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I{\i0} let him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, Ayase. I'm the one who let him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Endlave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The riots have reached us too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. That's a military machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What the hell is this about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you to fight! Let's get you somewhere safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't {\i1}want{\i0} to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cut my connection!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:16:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to make me into a slacker too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai gave me legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legs that could run fast anywhere, jump any height.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good! I can't let it end this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Shu. Let me stand on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone head for the old college building!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menjo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:17:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sweet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai, I'm moving forward too. Even if you're not here, I'll go forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shoot you! For real!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Aya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you were useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, what the hell is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1} ♪ Blooming wildflower ♪{just use the old TL we have for this song}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1} ♪ I beg you, please tell me ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1} ♪ Why do people fight and hurt each other? ♪ {Goes through next 3 lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since I ran full-tilt on my own legs like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little better too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, I was just overthinking things before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:20:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept what happened to Gai yet, but I want to think it through little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to think about what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey everybody! The TV's back on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transferring the feed to the monitors...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In our investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have been unable to find any survivors within the Loop 7 area who aren't highly cancerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The provisional government and GHQ have thus agreed to cease rescue operations
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and completely seal off the area for the next ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loop 7?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're inside Loop 7!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will devote our utmost efforts to eradicating the Apocalypse Virus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thereby dispel the concerns of the international community.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the newly inaugurated President of Japan's provisional government,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it is my duty to bring about rebirth via purification.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{New ED Here}
